"For months now, we have been finding these 
plans in the workers' clothing. What do they mean?"

36
00:36:25,352 --> 00:36:32,626
"At two -- at the end of this shift.
She has called another meeting."

37
00:38:59,106 --> 00:39:05,712
"These are the plans of the ancient catacombs 
-- far below the lowest levels of the workers' city."

38
00:39:54,061 --> 00:39:57,164
"What is down there that interests the workers?"

39
00:41:07,663 --> 00:41:15,236
"Today I will tell you the story of the Tower of Babel."

40
00:44:57,230 --> 00:45:03,203
"Let us build a tower whose summit will touch the skies--"

41
00:45:09,176 --> 00:45:18,185
"-- and on it we will inscribe: 'Great is
the world and its Creator. And great is Man.'"

42
