43
00:48:10,991 --> 00:48:18,999
"Between the brain that plans and the 
hands that build there must be a mediator."

44
00:48:20,901 --> 00:48:26,640
"It is the heart that must bring about 
an understanding between them."

45
00:49:07,080 --> 00:49:11,652
"But where is our mediator, Maria?"

46
00:49:34,174 --> 00:49:38,879
"Be patient, he will surely come."

47
00:49:57,764 --> 00:50:03,003
"We will wait, but not for long."

48
00:50:33,266 --> 00:50:40,507
"Rotwang, make your Robot in the 
likeness of that girl."

49
